title: Dethkarz for tunngle
description:
Dethkarz is a game that made in 1998, i consider it a game before its time pretty much as was myth2 and warzone2100.

The graphics in Dethkarz is good even by today's standards.

The upload is a RIP meaning no videos are present the torrent was created to quickly share the game so fellow tunnglers can receive it and resurrect its multiplayer.

The game supports up to 8 human players and 12 AI racers at the same time in the same race.

Feel free to contact me on tunngle -sydykov

have fun gaming people!
